  "title": "Assistant Software Engineer (PLC / SCADA)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Overview</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Assist the Senior and Software Engineers</li>\n  <li>Assist on configuration either on PLC or Scada</li>\n  <li>Prepare documentation</li>\n  <li>T&amp;C involvement</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities and Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To work with the Senior and Software Engineers on the task given</li>\n  <li>To ensure all the work given from the Senior and Software Engineers fulfill according to the senior instruction</li>\n  <li>To configure IO points in the PLC or SCADA</li>\n  <li>To Built database</li>\n  <li>To Built static graphics</li>\n  <li>To assist on the testing and commissioning</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Nitec/Higher Nitec/ Diploma in Computer Engineering or Electrical and Electronic Engineering or Mechatronics</li>\n  <li>At least minimum 1 years of relevant working experience</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of reading Logics and other Programming Languages</li>\n  <li>Down to earth, willing to learn, hardworking and willing to work overtime</li>\n</ul>",
